00:31:38,641 --> 00:31:42,241
So, Zosima, that's when Zosima passes it on.

323
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:44,401
But let's go back.

324
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:48,401
Now we hear Zosima was an almost savage creature.

325
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:50,160
He strikes his orderly.

326
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:53,361
That's on 336 and 339.

