00:31:57,921 --> 00:32:05,000
And then we better read what happens, what he says on 342, because he's channeling, in effect, Markle at that point.

331
00:32:05,401 --> 00:32:08,521
It suddenly dawns on him.

332
00:32:08,521 --> 00:32:10,121
It takes him over.

333
00:32:10,840 --> 00:32:12,841
340.

