00:35:24,641 --> 00:35:28,080
But he gives it a philosophical slant.

370
00:35:28,081 --> 00:35:35,081
He says, much on earth is hidden, and so forth and so forth, but we've got a mystical sense of our living bond with the other world.

371
00:35:35,081 --> 00:35:38,921
Now comes the problem with the higher heavenly world.

