00:35:41,481 --> 00:35:44,840
Is there a higher heavenly world that we're connected to?

374
00:35:46,121 --> 00:35:46,760
It's here.

375
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:47,400
It's now.

376
00:35:47,401 --> 00:35:47,800
Good.

377
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:48,360
Okay.

378
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:49,081
Yes.

379
00:35:49,081 --> 00:35:50,360
We are in paradise.

380
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:53,160
We are in heaven here and now if we could only see it.

