00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:09,080
So let me go on there.

384
00:36:10,041 --> 00:36:14,841
The higher heavenly world and the roots of our thoughts and feeling are not here, but in other worlds.

385
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:19,561
That's why the philosophers say that we can't understand the reality of things on earth.

386
00:36:19,561 --> 00:36:21,160
Very bad, very bad.

387
00:36:21,160 --> 00:36:29,801
It's true that the philosophers can't understand the reality of things on earth, but that shows that they're wrong, not that we should believe it.

